.TH SLERMES 1 "2026-05-25" "WuBu Slermes Agent" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
slermes \- AI agent CLI for conversation and tool execution
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B slermes
[\fIoptions\fR] [\fImessage\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Slermes is the C translation of the Hermes AI agent. It runs as a CLI
for conversation, tool execution, and gateway messaging.
.SH COMMANDS
.B init
Create default config.yaml and .env template.
.P
.B doctor
Run system diagnostics (config, API keys, version).
.P
.B completions
Generate shell completion scripts (bash, zsh, install).
.SH FILES
.I ~/.slermes/config.yaml
User configuration.
.P
.I ~/.slermes/.env
Environment variables (API keys).
.SH SEE ALSO
GitHub: https://github.com/waefrebeorn/hermes-agent
